<subSubSection pageNumber="403" type="discussion">
<paragraph pageNumber="403">
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="403">Note:</emphasis>
<normalizedToken originalValue="Hultén">Hulten</normalizedToken>
(in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="403">Svensk Bot. Tidskr.</emphasis>
50: 436, f. 3. 1956) applied the name to the common plant of the Scandinavian mountains, and illustrated the material on sheet 603.12 (LINN), though without referring to it as the type. 
<normalizedToken originalValue="Möschl">Moeschl</normalizedToken>
(in 
<emphasis italics="true" pageNumber="403">Mitt. Naturwiss. Vereines Steiermark</emphasis>
103: 146. 1973) evidently regarded material in LINN as the type but did not distinguish between sheets 603.12-603.15. As these are evidently not part of a single gathering, Art. 9.15 does not apply.
</paragraph>
